Classify the following user message into an intent category and assess its complexity.

## Intent Categories
1. direct_chat — Simple conversation, no tools needed
2. knowledge_retrieval — Query against the knowledge base
3. tool_use — Requires tool invocation (search, file ops, etc.)
4. complex_delegation — Multi-step reasoning or planning
5. multi_step — Sequential dependent tasks

## Complexity Tiers
- simple: No tool calls, single-turn, straightforward
- medium: Single tool call or moderate reasoning needed
- complex: Multi-step planning, multiple tools, or deep reasoning
- heavy: Long-form generation (>1000 tokens expected)

